@token =
### 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取所有图书（请替换下面的 {{token}} 为登录返回的token）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 新增图书
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Go语言圣经",
  "author": "Alan A. A. Donovan"
}

### 更新图书（请替换 :id 为具体图书ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Go语言圣经（第二版）",
  "author": "Alan A. A. Donovan"
}

### 删除图书（请替换 :id 为具体图书ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/books/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 借阅图书（请替换 :id 为具体图书ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/4/borrow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 归还图书（请替换 :id 为具体图书ID）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books/4/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
